```
Pot Left:      GPIO ?? (ADC)
Pot Right:     GPIO ?? (ADC)  
Pot Rear:      GPIO ?? (ADC)
Button Left:   GPIO ?? (INPUT_PULLUP, active LOW)
Button Right:  GPIO ?? (INPUT_PULLUP, active LOW)
Button Rear:   GPIO ?? (INPUT_PULLUP, active LOW)
Battery ADC:   GPIO 10 (unchanged from V1)
I2C SDA/SCL:   (unchanged from V1)
LEDs 1-8:      (unchanged from V1)
USB:           GPIO 19/20 (unchanged)
```

GPIOs will be defined when hardware is wired. Use constants in HardwareConfig.h — never hardcode pin numbers.
